data.description: Welcome to this amazing home with over 2500 square feet of living space and a large inviting front porch in the Franklinton area.  Walking distance to Columbus Metro Library, 4 minutes to the local popular brewery, 10 minutes to OSU campus and less than 10 minutes to downtown Columbus. Off street parking in the front and rear of the home.  The first floor features a dining space, two large living areas, original decorative fireplaces, half bath, large  mudroom, first floor laundry and an updated kitchen. Second floor features 5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  The primary bedroom/bathroom offers a nice walk-in closet with the other 4 bedrooms sharing a hall bathroom.  Fenced in backyard with patio and storage.  Schedule a showing today!
